[


               The prisoner was recommended to mercy by the prosecutor
            ].

Q. (to
Elizabeth Hancock
) By your mistresses directions you ran after this man did you. - A. Yes.

Court Q. (to
Ann Cutler
) I understand you to say, that the prisoner was at work at the upper rooms. - A. Yes.

Q. (to
Ann Cutler
) Was there any other person at work with him. - A. Yes.

Q. (to
Ann Cutler
) He did not return to work after Monday, did he. - A. No.
